{"tid":2513302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞送嘅威露士係支那牌扮德國貨！！大家咪買！！！！！","createTime":"2021-05-02T11:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T14:51:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":165,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"ec34c9b1756e4a3a45536911b236d3fba2224896","tid":2513302,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:47:44.000Z","msg":"已經有人中招了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fKTJhLu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfKTJhLu.png&h=13c45d2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vx0LsOn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvx0LsOn.png&h=cb361634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麥當勞最近推出左買兩個早餐就可以換一個濕鳩泡泡液，就算換到贈品(左)，長遠都要買梘液(右)!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dfQO911.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdfQO911.png&h=15e16cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">▸商家背景◂ 偽德國！威露士來自中國！</span></span><br />\n <br />\n最近疫情之下，賣廣告賣得好勁，標榜來自德國嘅威露士，實情係中國公司，由中國商人左大維於 2000 年喺廣州成立<br />\n <br />\n自稱來自德國，但喺歐洲嘅商標就 2003 年先註冊，仲要有一間叫 Lohmann Haas Pharmaceuticals (CHINA) Limited 嘅公司註冊<br />\n <br />\n為咗扮德國公司扮得更徹底，2019 年 8 月，威露士母公司收購咗一間 1904 年開業叫 Centralin 嘅德國嘅鞋油公司，自此威露士産品就多咗 Centralin 商標及「Germany since 1904」字樣，收購後 Centralin 商標有作出微調，加咗兩粒疑似影射美國莊臣舊商標 &quot;J&quot; 入面嘅圖形<br />\n <br />\n而廣告所指嘅「德國品牌」或 「Germany since 1904」係指收購返來嘅 Centralin 品牌，並非威露士<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"pink\">每次見到巴士大大隻 「快人一泡，德國品牌 」就覺得好賤，明明係大陸野喺度扮德國品牌，其實上面細細隻寫住係佢哋收購centralin 鞋油品牌先係德國品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"73b6406d79c73492efe208aaae7ffcd82006f746","tid":2513302,"uid":107217,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"我只係知間間都爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecd83ee39a18b9b8a2a3df026cbd7ba20d26df7","tid":2513302,"uid":39218,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係由小學聽個brand到而家先知<br />\n小學嗰陣聽嘅廣告歌仲上口到而家都仲記得<br />\n威露士我用威露士<br />\n齊齊洗手更容易<br />\n擠出泡泡好方便<br />\n泡泡泡泡泡<br />\n媽咪抱抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家知道左真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be75e56024cbf238ff7fd66d0bebd40ff23da3ca","tid":2513302,"uid":49285,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:55:20.000Z","msg":"支那野係咁<br />\nMiniso名創優品明明係支那 但又寫住Japanese Designer Brand<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361787d266de0b2ee08bed4b75574a0ca063cfac","tid":2513302,"uid":22675,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"be75e56024cbf238ff7fd66d0bebd40ff23da3ca","tid":2513302,"uid":49285,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:55:20.000Z","msg":"支那野係咁<br />\nMiniso名創優品明明係支那 但又寫住Japanese Designer Brand<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-