，長遠都要買梘液(右)!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dfQO911.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdfQO911.png&h=15e16cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">▸商家背景◂ 偽德國！威露士來自中國！</span></span><br />\n <br />\n最近疫情之下，賣廣告賣得好勁，標榜來自德國嘅威露士，實情係中國公司，由中國商人左大維於 2000 年喺廣州成立<br />\n <br />\n自稱來自德國，但喺歐洲嘅商標就 2003 年先註冊，仲要有一間叫 Lohmann Haas Pharmaceuticals (CHINA) Limited 嘅公司註冊<br />\n <br />\n為咗扮德國公司扮得更徹底，2019 年 8 月，威露士母公司收購咗一間 1904 年開業叫 Centralin 嘅德國嘅鞋油公司，自此威露士産品就多咗 Centralin 商標及「Germany since 1904」字樣，收購後 Centralin 商標有作出微調，加咗兩粒疑似影射美國莊臣舊商標 &quot;J&quot; 入面嘅圖形<br />\n <br />\n而廣告所指嘅「德國品牌」或 「Germany since 1904」係指收購返來嘅 Centralin 品牌，並非威露士<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"pink\">每次見到巴士大大隻 「快人一泡，德國品牌 」就覺得好賤，明明係大陸野喺度扮德國品牌，其實上面細細隻寫住係佢哋收購centralin 鞋油品牌先係德國品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T13:56:53.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"383760357d8f83567797af0b9df2c0c54e245078","tid":2513302,"uid":79510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"用過佢D手洗洗衣液<br />\n手掌會甩皮,手指起粒粒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434906da8d55a9d45758e969d897f46d0bbe471d","tid":2513302,"uid":61282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:04:58.000Z","msg":"記得反送中嗰期都有人提過"},{"pid":"f28d7a65b85480fc80a17fab790bf770b2cf0364","tid":2513302,"uid":65429,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:09:08.000Z","msg":"ON9<br />\n姜B代言,就算支那貨我都照買"},{"pid":"97b37e370e116440959ca69060c3766689ddfa78","tid":2513302,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:10:10.000Z","msg":"cls竟然係咁"},{"pid":"45757c8868b94327ab53dfe0a7db0c26e45f8cc1","tid":2513302,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dr